M|Lear|Quin|
M|Lear|1. *|** append to MEMORY.md — `[date] — feature — verdict — bug patterns found`
M|Lear|2. *|** add it to the QA checklist permanently — it's a systemic pattern, not a one-off
M|Lear|3. *|** Every Friday, pick one random output from each layer. Score Green/Yellow/Red. Patterns across Pulse reports identify systemic drift.
M|Lear|4. *|** log it w/ the risk that was accepted — if that risk materialises later, it validates the gate
M|Lear|5. *|** flag it to the spec author and log the clarity gap — bad AC is a process bug
